1. *Skinuo* je kaput i okačio ga na klin. (He *took off* his coat and hung it on the nail.)
2. Videla sam kako je *skinuo* šešir i pokazao mi svoju novu frizuru. (I saw him *take off* his hat and show me his new hairstyle.)
3. Kada je *skinula* masku, otkrila je da je to bila moja drugarica. (When she *took off* her mask, she revealed that it was my friend.)
4. Čovek koji je *skinuo* zastavu je uhapšen zbog kršenja javnog reda i mira. (The man who *lowered* the flag was arrested for disturbing the public peace.)
5. *Skinuo* sam pesmu sa interneta i sačuvao je na svom računaru. (I *downloaded* the song from the internet and saved it on my computer.)
6. Kada je počela kiša, *skinuo* je sa drveta sve jabuke koje su bile zrele. (When it started raining, he *picked off* all the ripe apples from the tree.)
7. On je glumac koji je *skinuo* nekoliko kilograma kako bi se što bolje uklopio u ulogu. (He is an actor who *lost* a few kilograms to fit into his role better.)
8. Kad sam videla taj novi par cipela, odmah sam ih *skinula* sa police i otišla da ih probam. (When I saw those new pair of shoes, I immediately *took* them off the shelf and went to try them on.)